text: Aymet Uzcátegui (, born 1 December 1995) is a Venezuelan tennis player. She has won five doubles titles on the ITF Women's Circuit, and made her debut for the Venezuela Fed Cup team in 2015, currently holding an 8–8 win-loss record.
